sequenceDiagram
    participant cam as RealSense D455
    participant rs as realsense2_camera
    participant aria as RosAria
    participant rec as record_data.py
    participant disk as ./data/

    cam->>rs: USB 3.x — raw frame
    rs->>rec: /camera/color/image_raw<br/>(sensor_msgs/Image)

    aria->>rec: /RosAria/pose<br/>(nav_msgs/Odometry)
    aria->>rec: /RosAria/cmd_vel<br/>(geometry_msgs/Twist)

    Note over rec: Callbacks store latest values in memory.<br/>Main loop fires every 1/1.5 s.

    rec->>rec: cv_bridge → numpy array
    rec->>rec: cv2.resize(320 × 240)
    rec->>rec: cv2.imwrite(JPEG, quality=95)

    rec->>disk: images/000042.jpg
    rec->>disk: frames.jsonl ← {stamp, odom, cmd}
